downloadDescription: Quickly create a highly visual event space plan with this Visio 2010 template.
detailsSection: Use this Microsoft Visio 2010 template to quickly create a highly visual event space plan. This template includes room layouts for a conference and a wedding reception, as well as sample Microsoft Excel reports to help track details such as seating assignments with meal preferences and special needs as well as an equipment inventory for the event. It provides custom shapes ranging from tables and chairs to sound equipment to help you quickly map out the layout for your event. This template could also be extended to help plan other types of events, including concerts or public meetings.
installInstructionSection: Click Download to save the template to your computer.
